# Sample JSONs for Config Files

## Promo JSON

```
{
  "promo": true,
  "percentage": 50,
  "expiry-date": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "translations": {
    "en": "Unlock all features forever with our holiday sale!",
    "ja": "ホリデーセールで全機能を永久にロック解除しましょう！"
  }
}
```

### Announcements JSON

```
[
  {
    "id": "sync-notice-001",
    "isActive": true,
    "type": "warning",
    "url": "https://pandesalbytes.ca/support",
    "translations": {
      "en": {
        "title": "CloudKit Sync Notice",
        "message": "We are currently investigating an issue where some iOS 18 users experience delayed syncing. A fix is in progress."
      },
      "ja": {
        "title": "CloudKit 同期に関するお知らせ",
        "message": "一部のiOS 18ユーザーで同期が遅れる問題を現在調査中です。修正作業を進めています。"
      }
    }
  }
]
```
